channel.title: PORTFORWARDING to put my sever online! O: help plz
channel.description:
okay , ive been having trouble with port forwarding but i know how to port forward it sorta because when i check to see if its online at canyouseeme.org it keeps saying "Error: I could not see your service on (my computer ip) on port (43594) Reason: Connection timed out
any ideas to fix this? thanks!!! (:

item.title: PORTFORWARDING to put my sever online! O: help plz
item.dc:creator: @dragon39990 dragon39990
item.description:
@dragon39990 wrote:

[quote=“Gypsy, post:5, topic:335862”]Post your router information.

Default gateway is 192.168.1.1 in a lot of cases

Type: 192.168.1.1 in your web browser

When you do that enter your username and password

Go to the portforwarding section

open the port TCP 43594

This site helps a ton: http://portforward.com/[/quote]

Mines 192.168.2.1 and I no people with 10.0.0.1 so its not 192.168.1.1 in most cases.
